Social Music sites are places where people meet online because they share music as their common interest. A few of these sites are listed below:



* '''Last FM''' [http://www.last.fm] - Last FM has grown from an experiment to a worldwide used network of music lovers.
* '''Myspace''' [http://www.myspace.com] - owned by Rupert Murdock, this site is wordwide known for its networking abilities, and used by many artists.


